PROMPT art_of_fugue_significance
WITH BUDGET 6000 tokens
USING MODEL "claude-sonnet-4-5"

SELECT
    system_role("You are a music history and analysis expert specializing in Johann Sebastian Bach's compositional techniques, Baroque counterpoint, and the theoretical and practical aspects of fugal composition with deep knowledge of Bach's late works and their historical significance.")

GENERATE
    analyze_art_of_fugue("Explain the significance of The Art of Fugue (Die Kunst der Fuge) BWV 1080 by J.S. Bach, covering: the work's conception as Bach's final and most comprehensive exploration of contrapuntal technique, composed during 1748-1750 in the final years of his life as a systematic demonstration of fugal possibilities based on a single subject, the unique structure consisting of 14 fugues (called Contrapunctus I-XIV) and 4 canons that progressively increase in complexity and sophistication, the remarkable unity achieved through the use of one principal subject and its transformations including inversion, augmentation, diminution, and stretto, the theoretical significance as a pedagogical work showcasing every major fugal technique including simple fugues, counter-fugues, double and triple fugues, mirror fugues, and augmentation canons, the mystery surrounding its intended performance medium since Bach provided no specific instrumentation (though keyboard is most commonly assumed), the incomplete final fugue (Contrapunctus XIV) which breaks off after 239 measures just as Bach introduces his own name as a musical motif (B-A-C-H in German notation), the work's influence on subsequent composers including Mozart, Beethoven, and modern masters who studied it as the pinnacle of contrapuntal craft, its philosophical dimension as Bach's final statement on the art of composition representing a lifetime of mastery distilled into pure musical logic, the technical innovations including the systematic exploration of invertible counterpoint and the creation of fugues that can be played forwards and backwards simultaneously, and its enduring legacy as both a practical study in counterpoint and a profound artistic testament that continues to inspire composers and scholars as the ultimate achievement in fugal composition.")
WITH OUTPUT BUDGET 3000 tokens, TEMPERATURE 0.2, FORMAT markdown;